### Variáveis (ajustar)
@base = https://<functionAppName>.azurewebsites.net
@key = <function_key>

### check-id (GET)
GET {{base}}/api/check-id?id=<sha256_hex_64>&source=openai&published_date=2026-04-05
x-functions-key: {{key}}

### check-id (POST)
POST {{base}}/api/check-id
Content-Type: application/json
x-functions-key: {{key}}

{
  "id": "<sha256_hex_64>",
  "source": "openai",
  "published_date": "2026-04-05"
}

### Resposta esperada (check-id)
# { "exists": false, "id": "<sha256>" }

### process (POST)
POST {{base}}/api/process
Content-Type: application/json
x-functions-key: {{key}}

{
  "date": "2026-04-05",
  "lookback_days": 1,
  "archive": false
}

### Resposta esperada (process)
# {
#   "ok": true,
#   "date": "2026-04-05",
#   "processed_count": 12,
#   "report_path": "daily-report-2026-04-05.json",
#   "processing_run_id": "..."
# }

### report (GET)
GET {{base}}/api/report?date=2026-04-05
x-functions-key: {{key}}

### Resposta esperada (report)
# Corpo = JSON do relatório (ver docs/schemas.md)
